	ust have a ticket regardless of age. No babies in arms. Mobile ticket deli
	very will be delayed until 4 days prior to event.\nMetal detectors & bag s
	earch at door. Arrive early. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety 
	When purchasing ADA accessible seating\, please feel free to contact us by
	 email if assistance is needed with accommodations or companion seating\; 
	you may reach us at accessibility@stgpresents.org. Each accessible seat ho
	uses an armless freestanding chair for patrons with mobility impairments a
	nd their companions. Please note that our historic theatre has no elevator
	 to the balcony levels. The ADA section on the seating map does not repres
	ent a specific seat location.\n\nhttps://www.ticketmaster.com/soen-dark-tr
